answer_sql: SELECT MAX(`Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)`) AS HighestEligibleFreeRate FROM frpm WHERE `County Name` = 'Alameda';
SELECT T1.Phone FROM schools AS T1 JOIN frpm AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T2.`Charter School (Y/N)` = 1 AND T1.OpenDate > '2000-01-01';
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT satscores.cds) AS num_schools FROM satscores JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools.CDSCode WHERE satscores.AvgScrMath < 400 AND schools.Virtual = 'F';

SELECT s.CDSCode, s.School, s.Street, s.City, s.State, s.Latitude, s.Longitude, s.AdmFName1, s.AdmLName1, s.AdmEmail1, s.LastUpdate FROM schools s JOIN frpm f ON s.CDSCode = f.CDSCode JOIN satscores sa ON s.CDSCode = sa.cds WHERE sa.NumTstTakr > 500 AND (s.Magnet = 1 OR s.GSoffered = 'Magnet')
SELECT COUNT(satscores.NumTstTakr) AS NumSATTestTakers FROM satscores JOIN frpm ON satscores.cds = frpm.CDSCode WHERE frpm.`Enrollment (K-12)` = (SELECT MAX(`Enrollment (K-12)`) FROM frpm)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT sc.CDSCode) AS charter_funded_schools FROM satscores AS s JOIN schools AS sc ON s.cds = sc.CDSCode WHERE s.AvgScrMath > 560 AND sc.FundingType = 'Charter'
SELECT MAX(frm.`Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)`) AS max_eligible_free_rate FROM frpm frm JOIN satscores ss ON frm.CDSCode = ss.cds WHERE ss.NumGE1500 / ss.NumTstTakr > 0.3;
SELECT s.CDSCode, s.Street, s.City, s.State, s.Phone FROM schools s JOIN frpm f ON s.CDSCode = f.CDSCode JOIN satscores sa ON s.CDSCode = sa.cds ORDER BY sa.NumGE1500 / sa.NumTstTakr DESC LIMIT 3;

SELECT s.CDSCode, AVG(sc.AvgScrRead) AS AvgScore FROM schools s JOIN frpm f ON s.CDSCode = f.CDSCode JOIN satscores sc ON s.CDSCode = sc.cds WHERE s.StatusType = 'Active' GROUP BY s.CDSCode ORDER BY AvgScore DESC LIMIT 1;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS num_schools FROM schools AS s JOIN frpm AS fr ON s.CDSCode = fr.CDSCode WHERE s.County = 'Alameda' AND fr.`Enrollment (K-12)` < 100;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS num_schools FROM frpm WHERE `Free Meal Count (K-12)` > 500 AND `Free Meal Count (K-12)` < 700;
SELECT s.CDSCode, s.School, COUNT(satscores.cds) AS NumTstTakr FROM schools s JOIN satscores ON s.CDSCode = satscores.cds GROUP BY s.CDSCode, s.School ORDER BY NumTstTakr DESC LIMIT 1;
SELECT s.FundingType FROM frpm f JOIN schools s ON f.CDSCode = s.CDSCode JOIN satscores sa ON f.CDSCode = sa.cds WHERE sa.AvgScrMath > 400 ORDER BY s.FundingType;

SELECT s.School, AVG(sc.AvgScrWrite) AS AvgScrWrite, CASE WHEN s.Phone IS NOT NULL THEN s.Phone ELSE NULL END AS Phone FROM schools s JOIN satscores sc ON s.CDSCode = sc.cds WHERE s.OpenDate > '1991-12-31' OR s.ClosedDate < '2000-12-31' GROUP BY s.School

SELECT satscores.cds AS cds, satscores.sname AS school_name, schools.website AS website_address FROM satscores JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools.CDSCode WHERE satscores.enroll12 BETWEEN 1900 AND 2000 AND satscores.enroll12 > 1900 AND satscores.enroll12 < 2000
SELECT s.website FROM schools s JOIN frpm f ON s.CDSCode = f.CDSCode JOIN satscores sa ON s.CDSCode = sa.cds WHERE sa.enroll12 BETWEEN 2000 AND 3000;
SELECT AVG(satscores.NumTstTakr) FROM satscores JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools.CDSCode WHERE schools.OpenDate BETWEEN '1980-01-01' AND '1980-12-31';
SELECT T1.Phone FROM schools AS T1 JOIN satscores AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.cds WHERE T1.District = 'Fresno Unified' ORDER BY T2.AvgScrRead LIMIT 1;

SELECT s.School, AVG(sc.AvgScrRead) AS AvgReadScore FROM schools s JOIN frpm f ON s.CDSCode = f.CDSCode JOIN satscores sc ON s.CDSCode = sc.cds WHERE s.Virtual = 'F' GROUP BY s.School ORDER BY AvgReadScore DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT satscores.cds, AVG(satscores.AvgScrMath) AS AvgMathScore, schools.County FROM satscores JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools.CDSCode GROUP BY satscores.cds, schools.County ORDER BY AvgMathScore ASC LIMIT 1;

SELECT satscores.cds, satscores.sname, satscores.dname, satscores.cname, satscores.enroll12, satscores.NumTstTakr, satscores.AvgScrWrite FROM satscores JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools.CDSCode WHERE satscores.NumTstTakr >= 1500 ORDER BY satscores.NumTstTakr DESC LIMIT 1;

SELECT COUNT(schools.CDSCode) / 12 AS MonthlyAverageSchools FROM schools JOIN schools_admins ON schools.CDSCode = schools_admins.CDSCode WHERE schools.District = 'Elementary School District' AND schools.OpenDate BETWEEN '1980-01-01' AND '1980-12-31' AND schools.DOC = 52;
SELECT COUNT(CASE WHEN DOC = 52 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) / COUNT(CASE WHEN DOC = 54 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS Ratio FROM schools WHERE DOC IN (52, 54)

SELECT s.County, s.School, s.ClosedDate FROM schools s JOIN frpm f ON s.CDSCode = f.CDSCode WHERE s.StatusType LIKE '%Closed%' AND s.ClosedDate IS NOT NULL GROUP BY s.County, s.School, s.ClosedDate ORDER BY COUNT(f.CDSCode) DESC LIMIT 1;
SELECT schools.School AS SchoolName, schools.Street AS PostalStreetAddress FROM schools WHERE schools.School = ( SELECT sname FROM satscores ORDER BY AvgScrMath DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 5 )

SELECT satscores.cds, satscores.sname, schools.Street FROM satscores JOIN frpm ON satscores.cds = frpm.CDSCode JOIN schools ON frpm.CDSCode = schools.CDSCode ORDER BY satscores.AvgScrRead ASC LIMIT 1;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s.CDSCode) AS TotalSchools FROM schools s JOIN satscores ss ON s.CDSCode = ss.cds JOIN schools_admins sa ON s.CDSCode = sa.CDSCode WHERE sa.City = 'Lakeport' AND ss.AvgScrRead + ss.AvgScrMath + ss.AvgScrWrite >= 1500;

SELECT COUNT(s2.enroll12) AS test_takers
FROM schools s1
JOIN schools_admins sa ON s1.CDSCode = sa.CDSCode
JOIN satscores s2 ON s1.CDSCode = s2.cds
WHERE sa.City = 'Fresno'

SELECT COUNT(CASE WHEN T2.State = 'CA' THEN T1.CDSCode ELSE NULL END) / COUNT(CASE WHEN T2.State = 'CA' THEN T2.CDSCode ELSE NULL END) AS Ratio FROM schools AS T1 JOIN schools_admins AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T2.State = 'CA';

SELECT COUNT(*) AS Active_Schools FROM schools WHERE State = 'CA' AND (MailState IS NULL OR MailState = 'CA') AND (ClosedDate IS NULL OR ClosedDate >= '1900-01-01') AND (OpenDate IS NULL OR OpenDate <= '1900-01-01') AND (Magnet = 0);
SELECT Website FROM schools WHERE Virtual = 'P' AND Charter = 1 AND County = 'San Joaquin';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS chartered_schools FROM schools JOIN schools_admins ON schools.CDSCode = schools_admins.CDSCode WHERE schools.District = 52 AND schools.Charter = 1 AND schools.City = 'Hickman';

SELECT COUNT(*) AS Total_Schools FROM schools JOIN schools_admins ON schools.CDSCode = schools_admins.CDSCode JOIN frpm ON schools.CDSCode = frpm.CDSCode WHERE schools.StreetAbr = 'HICKMAN' AND schools.Charter = 0 AND schools.CharterNum = '00D4';
SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN FundingType = 'Local' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(CASE WHEN FundingType = 'Local' THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS Ratio FROM schools WHERE County = 'Santa Clara';

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.CDSCode) AS DirectlyFundedSchools FROM frpm AS T1 JOIN schools AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T1.`Academic Year` BETWEEN '2000-01-01' AND '2005-12-31' AND T2.County = 'Stanislaus' AND T2.FundingType = 'Directly Funded';

SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN T1.CDSCode IN (SELECT T2.CDSCode FROM schools AS T2 WHERE T2.City = 'San Francisco' AND T2.StatusType = 'CCD' AND T2.ClosedDate <= '1989-12-31') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalCCDClosures FROM schools AS T1 WHERE T1.City = 'San Francisco' AND T1.StatusType = 'CCD' AND T1.ClosedDate <= '1989-12-31';
SELECT County FROM schools WHERE SOC = '11' AND OpenDate BETWEEN '1980-01-01' AND '1989-12-31' AND ClosedDate IS NOT NULL GROUP BY County ORDER BY COUNT(ClosedDate) DESC LIMIT 1;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN schools.StatusType = 'Active' THEN schools.District WHEN schools.StatusType = 'Closed' THEN schools.District ELSE NULL END) AS DistrictCommunityDaySchools FROM schools JOIN frpm ON schools.CDSCode = frpm.CDSCode WHERE schools.County = 'Alpine';
SELECT MIN(T2.`Low Grade`) AS LowestGrade FROM schools AS T1 JOIN frpm AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T1.EdOpsCode = 'SPECON' AND T1.NCESDist = '613360';
SELECT County FROM schools WHERE Virtual = 'F' GROUP BY County ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1;
SELECT schools.School, schools.Latitude FROM schools WHERE schools.Latitude = ( SELECT MAX(Latitude) FROM schools ) ORDER BY schools.Latitude DESC LIMIT 1;
SELECT 'Low Grade' AS GradeSpan FROM schools WHERE Longitude = ( SELECT MAX(Longitude) FROM schools );

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s1.CDSCode) AS schools_with_magnet_program, COUNT(DISTINCT s2.City) AS cities_with_k_to_8_span, s2.City AS city_name, COUNT(s2.CDSCode) AS schools_serving_k_to_8_span FROM schools s1 JOIN schools s2 ON s1.CDSCode = s2.CDSCode WHERE s1.Magnet = 1 AND s1.GSserved = 'K-8' GROUP BY s2.City;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT a.account_id) AS account_count FROM account a JOIN trans t ON a.account_id = t.account_id JOIN district d ON a.district_id = d.district_id WHERE d.A3 = 'POPLATEK PO OBRATU' AND d.A5 = 'East Bohemia';
SELECT COUNT(account_id) AS eligible_accounts FROM account WHERE district_id IN ( SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A3 = 'Prague' ) AND account_id IN ( SELECT account_id FROM loan )

SELECT district_id, AVG(A12) AS unemployment_1995, AVG(A13) AS unemployment_1996 FROM district WHERE A12 IS NOT NULL AND A13 IS NOT NULL GROUP BY district_id HAVING AVG(A12) > AVG(A13) ORDER BY AVG(A12) DESC;
SELECT COUNT(district_id) AS district_count FROM district WHERE A11 > 6000 AND A11 < 10000 AND district_id IN ( SELECT district_id FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' );

SELECT COUNT(T1.client_id) AS male_customers_count FROM client AS T1 JOIN district AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id JOIN account AS T3 ON T1.district_id = T3.district_id JOIN trans AS T4 ON T1.client_id = T4.account_id WHERE T1.gender = 'M' AND T2.A3 = 'North Bohemia' AND T3.frequency = 'Monthly' AND T4.type = 'Deposit' AND T4.balance > 8000;

SELECT DISTINCT T1.account_id FROM account AS T1 JOIN client AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id WHERE T2.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client) GROUP BY T1.account_id HAVING AVG(T1.frequency) = (SELECT MAX(average_salary) FROM (SELECT AVG(frequency) AS average_salary FROM account GROUP BY account_id)) ORDER BY T2.birth_date ASC;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.client_id) AS owner_count FROM client AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id JOIN trans AS T3 ON T1.client_id = T3.account_id WHERE T2.frequency = 'POPLATEK TYDNE' AND T1.gender = 'Owner';

SELECT a.account_id, a.district_id, a.frequency, a.date, l.amount, l.status FROM loan l JOIN account a ON l.account_id = a.account_id WHERE l.date BETWEEN '1997-01-01' AND '1997-12-31' ORDER BY l.amount ASC LIMIT 1;

SELECT t1.account_id, MAX(t2.amount) AS max_amount FROM account t1 JOIN loan t2 ON t1.account_id = t2.account_id WHERE t2.duration > 12 GROUP BY t1.account_id HAVING t1.date >= '1993-01-01' AND t1.date < '1994-01-01'

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c.client_id) AS female_customers_count FROM client c JOIN account a ON c.district_id = a.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date < '1950-01-01' AND a.district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A2 = 'Slokolov');
SELECT DISTINCT a.account_id, a.date FROM account a JOIN trans t ON a.account_id = t.account_id WHERE STRFTIME('%Y', t.date) = '1995' ORDER BY a.date ASC LIMIT 1;

SELECT DISTINCT a.account_id, a.district_id, a.frequency, a.date FROM account a JOIN loan l ON a.account_id = l.account_id JOIN trans t ON a.account_id = t.account_id WHERE a.date < '1997-01-01' AND l.amount > 3000
SELECT client.client_id FROM client JOIN disp ON client.client_id = disp.client_id JOIN card ON disp.disp_id = card.disp_id WHERE card.issued LIKE '1994-03-03';
SELECT DISTINCT T1.date, T2.date AS account_opened_date FROM trans AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.account_id = T2.account_id WHERE T1.amount = 840 AND T1.date = '1998-10-14';

SELECT MAX(trans.amount) AS max_amount FROM trans JOIN account ON trans.account_id = account.account_id JOIN client ON account.district_id = client.district_id JOIN disp ON account.account_id = disp.account_id JOIN card ON disp.disp_id = card.disp_id WHERE trans.date >= '1996-10-21' AND trans.type = 'IN';

SELECT DISTINCT T1.gender FROM client AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id JOIN trans AS T3 ON T2.account_id = T3.account_id JOIN district AS T4 ON T1.district_id = T4.district_id WHERE T4.A11 = ( SELECT MAX(T5.A11) FROM district AS T5 WHERE T5.district_id = T4.district_id ) ORDER BY T1.birth_date ASC LIMIT 1;

SELECT MIN(trans.amount) AS first_transaction_amount FROM trans JOIN loan ON trans.account_id = loan.account_id JOIN account ON trans.account_id = account.account_id WHERE loan.amount = (SELECT MAX(amount) FROM loan)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c.client_id) AS num_clients FROM client c JOIN district d ON c.district_id = d.district_id JOIN account a ON c.district_id = a.district_id JOIN disp d2 ON c.client_id = d2.client_id WHERE d.A2 = 'Jesenik' AND c.gender = 'F';
SELECT COUNT(account_id) AS account_count FROM account WHERE district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A2 = 'Litomerice') AND date = '1996-01-01';
SELECT T1.district_id FROM client AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.client_id = T2.account_id WHERE T1.gender = 'F' AND T1.birth_date = '1976-01-29';
SELECT T2.birth_date FROM loan AS T1 JOIN client AS T2 ON T1.account_id = T2.client_id WHERE T1.amount = 98832 AND T1.date = '1996-01-03';
SELECT account.account_id FROM account JOIN client ON account.district_id = client.district_id WHERE client.district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A3 = 'Prague') LIMIT 1;

SELECT CAST(COUNT(CASE WHEN T2.gender = 'M' THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(T2.client_id) AS percentage FROM district AS T1 JOIN client AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id WHERE T1.A3 = 'South Bohemia'

SELECT c.client_id, (SUM(t.amount) - SUM(t.amount)) / SUM(t.amount) * 100 AS increase_rate FROM client c JOIN account a ON c.district_id = a.district_id JOIN loan l ON a.account_id = l.account_id JOIN trans t ON a.account_id = t.account_id WHERE l.date >= '1993-07-05' AND t.date BETWEEN '1993-03-22' AND '1998-12-27' GROUP BY c.client_id ORDER BY increase_rate DESC;
SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'A' THEN amount ELSE 0 END) / SUM(amount) * 100 AS percentage FROM loan

SELECT (SUM(CASE WHEN T1.amount < 100000 AND T1.status = 'C' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(T1.amount)) AS percentage FROM loan AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.account_id = T2.account_id WHERE T2.district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM client WHERE client_id = (SELECT client_id FROM account WHERE account_id = T1.account_id))

SELECT a.account_id, d.A2 AS district_name, d.A3 AS district_region FROM account a JOIN district d ON a.district_id = d.district_id WHERE a.date BETWEEN '1993-01-01' AND '1993-12-31' AND a.frequency = 'POPLATEK PO OBRATU';

SELECT DISTINCT a.account_id FROM account a JOIN trans t ON a.account_id = t.account_id JOIN client c ON a.district_id = c.district_id WHERE t.date BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '2000-12-31' AND a.district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A3 = 'east Bohemia');
SELECT account_id, date FROM account WHERE district_id IN (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A2 = 'Prachatice')
SELECT district.A2, district.A3 FROM loan JOIN account ON loan.account_id = account.account_id JOIN district ON account.district_id = district.district_id WHERE loan.loan_id = '4990';

SELECT account.account_id, district.A2, district.A3 FROM loan JOIN account ON loan.account_id = account.account_id JOIN district ON account.district_id = district.district_id WHERE loan.amount > 300000;

SELECT l.loan_id, d.A3 AS district, AVG(d.A11) AS average_salary FROM loan l JOIN account a ON l.account_id = a.account_id JOIN district d ON a.district_id = d.district_id WHERE l.duration = 60 GROUP BY l.loan_id, d.A3 ORDER BY l.loan_id;

SELECT d.A2, d.A3, (A13 - A12) / A12 * 100 AS unemployment_increment_percentage FROM loan l JOIN account a ON l.account_id = a.account_id JOIN district d ON a.district_id = d.district_id WHERE l.status = 'D'

SELECT (COUNT(account_id) * 100.0 / (SELECT COUNT(account_id) FROM account WHERE district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A2 = 'Decin'))) AS percentage FROM account WHERE date BETWEEN '1993-01-01' AND '1993-12-31';
SELECT DISTINCT T1.account_id FROM trans AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.account_id = T2.account_id WHERE T2.frequency = 'POPLATEK MESICNE';

SELECT district.A2, COUNT(account.account_id) AS female_account_count FROM account JOIN client ON account.district_id = client.district_id JOIN district ON client.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' GROUP BY district.A2 ORDER BY female_account_count DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT d.A2 AS district_name, COUNT(t.type) AS withdrawals FROM trans t JOIN account a ON t.account_id = a.account_id JOIN district d ON a.district_id = d.district_id WHERE t.type = 'VYDAJ' AND t.date LIKE '1996-01%' AND t.type != 'KREDITE' GROUP BY d.A2 ORDER BY withdrawals DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT COUNT(account.account_id) AS no_credit_cards FROM account JOIN client ON account.district_id = client.district_id JOIN disp ON account.account_id = disp.account_id WHERE client.district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A3 = 'South Bohemia') AND account.district_id = client.district_id;

SELECT d.A3, MAX(l.amount) FROM district d JOIN account a ON d.district_id = a.district_id JOIN loan l ON a.account_id = l.account_id WHERE l.status = 'C' GROUP BY d.A3 ORDER BY MAX(l.amount) DESC LIMIT 1;
SELECT AVG(loan.amount) AS average_loan_amount FROM loan JOIN client ON loan.account_id = client.client_id WHERE client.gender = 'M';

SELECT DISTINCT d.A2, d.A3, d.A4, d.A5, d.A6, d.A7, d.A8, d.A9, d.A10, d.A11, d.A12, d.A13 FROM district d JOIN account a ON d.district_id = a.district_id JOIN trans t ON a.account_id = t.account_id WHERE t.date >= '1996-01-01' AND t.date < '1997-01-01' ORDER BY d.A13 DESC;
SELECT COUNT(account_id) AS account_count FROM account WHERE strftime('%Y', date) = '1996' GROUP BY district_id ORDER BY COUNT(account_id) DESC LIMIT 1;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT a.account_id) AS account_count FROM trans t JOIN account a ON t.account_id = a.account_id JOIN card c ON a.district_id = c.disp_id WHERE t.type = 'VYBER KARTOU' AND t.operation = 'POPLATEK MESICNE' AND t.balance < 0;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l.account_id) AS loan_count FROM loan l JOIN account a ON l.account_id = a.account_id WHERE a.frequency = 'POPLATEK MESICNE' AND l.amount >= 250000 AND l.status = 'APPROVED' AND l.date BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1997-12-31';

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT a.account_id) AS running_contract_accounts FROM account a JOIN loan l ON a.account_id = l.account_id WHERE l.status = 'C' OR l.status = 'D' AND a.district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A2 = 'Branch');

SELECT COUNT(T1.client_id) AS male_clients FROM client AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id WHERE T1.gender = 'M' AND T2.date BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY T1.client_id;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT card.card_id) AS high_level_credit_cards FROM card JOIN disp ON card.disp_id = disp.disp_id JOIN account ON disp.account_id = account.account_id WHERE card.type = 'gold' AND disp.type = 'disponent';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS account_count FROM district WHERE A2 = 'Pisek';
SELECT DISTINCT T2.district_id FROM trans AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.account_id = T2.account_id WHERE T1.amount > 10000 AND T1.date BETWEEN '1997-01-01' AND '1997-12-31';

SELECT DISTINCT T1.account_id FROM trans AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.account_id = T2.account_id WHERE T1.operation = 'VYBER KARTOU' AND T1.date >= '1998-01-01' AND T1.date < '1999-01-01' GROUP BY T1.account_id HAVING AVG(T1.amount) > (SELECT AVG(amount) FROM trans WHERE operation = 'VYBER KARTOU' AND date >= '1998-01-01' AND date < '1999-01-01')

SELECT DISTINCT T1.client_id, T1.gender FROM client AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id JOIN trans AS T3 ON T2.account_id = T3.account_id JOIN loan AS T4 ON T2.account_id = T4.account_id JOIN card AS T5 ON T2.account_id = T5.card_id WHERE T1.gender = 'F';

SELECT COUNT(account_id) AS female_clients_accounts FROM account JOIN client ON account.district_id = client.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND account.date BETWEEN '2020-01-01' AND '2020-12-31' AND client.district_id IN ( SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A3 = 'south Bohemia' );
SELECT disp.account_id FROM disp JOIN account ON disp.account_id = account.account_id JOIN district ON account.district_id = district.district_id WHERE district.A2 = 'Tabor' AND disp.type = 'OWNER';

SELECT DISTINCT t1.type FROM card t1 JOIN trans t2 ON t1.disp_id = t2.account_id JOIN account t3 ON t2.account_id = t3.account_id JOIN client t4 ON t3.district_id = t4.district_id JOIN district t5 ON t4.district_id = t5.district_id WHERE t1.type NOT IN (SELECT t1.type FROM loan t1 WHERE t1.account_id = t2.account_id) AND t5.A11 > 8000 AND t5.A11 <= 9000;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT a.account_id) AS account_count
FROM account a
JOIN trans t ON a.account_id = t.account_id
JOIN district d ON a.district_id = d.district_id
WHERE d.A3 = 'North Bohemia' AND t.bank = 'AB';
SELECT DISTINCT district.A2 FROM district JOIN account ON district.district_id = account.district_id JOIN trans ON account.account_id = trans.account_id WHERE trans.type = 'VYDAJ';

SELECT AVG(T1.A15) AS average_crimes FROM district AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id JOIN disp AS T3 ON T2.account_id = T3.account_id WHERE T1.A3 IN (SELECT T1.A3 FROM district AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id WHERE T2.date >= '1995-12-31' AND T2.frequency = 'Monthly') AND T2.date >= '1997-12-31' AND T2.frequency = 'Monthly';

SELECT COUNT(*) AS loan_eligible_cards FROM card WHERE card.type = 'CLASSIC' AND card.disp_id IN ( SELECT disp_id FROM disp WHERE account_id IN ( SELECT account_id FROM account WHERE frequency = 'OWNER' ) );
SELECT COUNT(T1.client_id) AS male_clients FROM client AS T1 JOIN district AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id WHERE T2.A2 = 'Hl.m. Praha' AND T1.gender = 'M';
SELECT (COUNT(CASE WHEN type = 'gold' AND issued < '1998-01-01' THEN card_id ELSE NULL END) / COUNT(card_id)) * 100 AS gold_card_percentage FROM card WHERE type = 'gold'

SELECT T1.client_id, T1.gender, T1.birth_date, T1.district_id FROM client AS T1 JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.district_id = T2.district_id JOIN loan AS T3 ON T2.account_id = T3.account_id WHERE T3.amount = (SELECT MAX(amount) FROM loan) ORDER BY T1.district_id ASC LIMIT 1;

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM trans AS T1 INNER JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.account_id = T2.account_id INNER JOIN district AS T3 ON T2.district_id = T3.district_id WHERE T3.A15 = 'committed crimes in 1995' AND T2.account_id = 532;
SELECT T2.district_id FROM `order` AS T1 INNER JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.account_id = T2.account_id WHERE T1.order_id = 33333;

SELECT t1.date, t1.type, t1.operation, t1.amount, t1.balance FROM trans AS t1 JOIN account AS t2 ON t1.account_id = t2.account_id JOIN client AS t3 ON t2.district_id = t3.district_id WHERE t1.type = 'VYBER' AND t3.client_id = 3356;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM account a JOIN loan l ON a.account_id = l.account_id WHERE a.frequency = 'POPLATEK TYDNE' GROUP BY a.account_id HAVING SUM(l.amount) < 200000;

SELECT (SUM(CASE WHEN T1.Currency = 'EUR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(T1.CustomerID)) AS Percentage FROM customers AS T1 JOIN transactions_1k AS T2 ON T1.CustomerID = T2.CustomerID WHERE T1.Segment = 'KAM';

SELECT CAST(COUNT(CASE WHEN Consumption > 528.3 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(CASE WHEN Consumption > 528.3 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS Percentage FROM yearmonth WHERE Date LIKE '201202%';

SELECT c.Segment FROM customers c JOIN yearmonth ym ON c.CustomerID = ym.CustomerID WHERE ym.Date = '201206' ORDER BY ym.Consumption ASC LIMIT 1;

SELECT AVG(Price) AS AverageTotalPrice FROM transactions_1k WHERE Date LIKE '2012-01%'
